chunks.text: When you go joyriding, which student would you like to end up like?
The one with no injuries, the one who is paralysed from the legs down, the one with the broken rest,
the one with the wet-lash, the one with glass in their head, or the one who's unconscious and never wakes up.
Oh my god, I'm out of the car, yeah!
Let's get out of the car!
Hey, my name is your name.
Hey, look, I know you're not getting you, you're not getting in your head.
